ActTobacco Act
SubjectTobacco Products Labelling Regulations (Cigarettes and Little Cigars)
PrecisTOBACCO PRODUCTS LABELLING REGULATIONS (Cigarettes and Little Cigars), in order to replace the labelling requirements for cigarettes and little cigars currently enshrined in the Tobacco Products Information Regulations with new messages that are more memorable, noticeable, and engaging.
